《'''性滿意足'''》（{{lang-en|''Satisfaction''}}）是一部在2014年7月17日晚間10點於[[USA電視台|USA電視台]]首播的影集。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/usa-network-summer-rush-satisfaction-royal-pains |title=USA Network Set Summer Premiere Dates |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=April 23, 2014 |access-date=2014-11-12 |archive-date=2014-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626215139/http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/usa-network-summer-rush-satisfaction-royal-pains/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>本劇獲得第二季續訂，並同樣預訂播出10集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/10/02/usa-network-renews-satisfaction-cancels-rush/|title=USA Network renews 'Satisfaction,' cancels 'Rush'|work=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|accessdate=24 August 2015|archive-date=2015-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114071339/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/10/02/usa-network-renews-satisfaction-cancels-rush/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年2月26日，USA宣布取消本劇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/satisfaction-canceled-usa-after-two-seasons-1201710182/|title=‘Satisfaction’ Canceled By USA After Two Seasons|work=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|date=February 26, 2016|accessdate=February 26, 2016|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301132341/https://deadline.com/2016/02/satisfaction-canceled-usa-after-two-seasons-1201710182/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 故事 ==
正當基金經理人尼爾（[[麥特·帕斯莫|麥特·帕斯莫]] 飾演）與妻子葛蕾絲（{{link-en|史黛芬妮·紹姿塔克|Stephanie Szostak}} 飾演）在面對他們之間的夫妻感情與和人生議題時，尼爾意外發現妻子與牛郎發生關係。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/usa-summer-premiere-dates-satisfaction-698323 |title=USA Debuts First Trailer for Matt Passmore's 'Satisfaction,' Set Summer Premieres |first=Denise |last=Petski |work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]] |date=April 23, 2014 |accessdate=2014-11-12 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003319/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/usa-summer-premiere-dates-satisfaction-698323 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在偶然的機會下，尼爾開始瞞著妻子當起牛郎，同時，尼爾也開始省思自己的婚姻與人生。

