== 製作 ==
本劇由尚恩·雅布朗斯基開創，並由勞斯·克雷斯納弗擔任執行製作。本劇取景於[[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/usa-network-sets-summer-premiere-dates-for-rush-satisfaction-and-returnees-1201161441 |title=USA Network Sets Summer Premiere Dates for 'Rush,' 'Satisfaction' and Returnees |last=Kissell |first=Rick |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]] |date=April 23, 2014 |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024310/https://variety.com/2014/tv/news/usa-network-sets-summer-premiere-dates-for-rush-satisfaction-and-returnees-1201161441/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

